%% Data Science Pipelines Operator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Dashboard
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Object Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant Envoy as MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant PipelinePod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(v2_component)

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Execution Request

    User->>Router: POST /apis/v1beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Router->>RBAC: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    RBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>RBAC: Authorized
    RBAC->>API: Forward request<br/>TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>DB credentials, TLS
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>S3 credentials, TLS
    API->>K8sAPI: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: Workflow CR created
    Argo->>PipelinePod: Execute pipeline step
    API-->>RBAC: Response
    RBAC-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over PA,DB: Flow 2: Pipeline Run Status Sync

    PA->>K8sAPI: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8sAPI-->>PA: Workflow status update
    PA->>API: Update run status<br/>8888/TCP, TLS (PodToPodTLS)
    API->>DB: Persist status<br/>DB credentials, TLS

    Note over PipelinePod,DB: Flow 3: MLMD Artifact Tracking

    PipelinePod->>MLMD: Log artifact/execution<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP, TLS
    MLMD->>DB: Store metadata<br/>DB credentials, TLS

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3b: External MLMD Access

    User->>Router: MLMD query<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    Router->>RBAC: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    RBAC->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>RBAC: Authorized
    RBAC->>Envoy: Forward to Envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC TLS
    Envoy->>MLMD: Forward gRPC<br/>8080/TCP TLS
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Response
    Envoy-->>RBAC: Response
    RBAC-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: gRPC Response
